citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:30-1:00pm on
10-FEB-21. Left a voicemail at the number on file as well as honked horn in driveway. No response was received within
30 minutes of initial arrival.
End Section
